You think...

552
00:23:43,531 --> 00:23:45,130
是的 她上了他
Yeah, she screwed him.

553
00:23:46,266 --> 00:23:48,466
毫无疑问
No doubt.

554
00:24:01,256 --> 00:24:04,123
我只是 只是还不敢相信
I just... just still don't believe it.

555
00:24:04,125 --> 00:24:06,159
两年了 发生了什么
Two years. What happened?

556
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:07,659
你去了哪里 为什么离开
Where'd you go? Why'd you leave?

557
00:24:07,661 --> 00:24:09,428
我不知道 我只是
I don't know, I was just...

558
00:24:09,430 --> 00:24:11,963
处理一些事情 你知道吗
dealing with some stuff, you know?

559
00:24:13,666 --> 00:24:14,999
事情 比如说
Stuff. Like what?

560
00:24:18,605 --> 00:24:20,972
说嘛 Sunny 我应该知道
Come on, I deserve to know, Sunny.

561
00:24:20,974 --> 00:24:22,273
你和我 我们曾如此亲密
You and me, we got close,

562
00:24:22,275 --> 00:24:25,944
然后你就消失了
and then you just... up and disappeared.

563
00:24:27,614 --> 00:24:30,280
你甚至没有说过再见
You never even said good-bye.

564
00:24:32,251 --> 00:24:35,886
我知道 对不起
I know. I'm sorry.

565
00:24:35,888 --> 00:24:37,687
尽管如此 你当时离开
It was probably a good thing

566
00:24:37,689 --> 00:24:39,389
可能是件好事
you left when you did, though.

567
00:24:39,391 --> 00:24:40,858
之后所有人都被捕了
Everybody got busted right afterwards.

568
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:42,860
很显然 有人背叛了我们
Apparently, somebody ratted us out.

569
00:24:42,862 --> 00:24:44,327
是的 但你没有被捕 不是吗
Yeah, but you didn't get busted, right?

570
00:24:44,329 --> 00:24:46,996
没有 多亏了你
No, thanks to you.

571
00:24:46,998 --> 00:24:48,564
关于这个叫
How much did Percy say

572
00:24:48,566 --> 00:24:51,000
-Ramon的家伙 Percy讲了多少 -显然不够多
- about this Ramon dude, exactly? - Not enough, obviously.

573
00:24:51,002 --> 00:24:52,501
嗯 但你没做什么错事儿吧
Yeah, but you didn't do anything wrong, right?

574
00:24:52,503 --> 00:24:54,871
你只是给他们修修摩托车 对吧
You were just building bikes for them, right?

575
00:24:54,873 --> 00:24:56,538
-差不多 -看起来Percy隐瞒的
- Yeah, pretty much. - Yo, looks like Percy's hiding

576
00:24:56,540 --> 00:24:57,673
还不只是勾搭的事
more than just a hook-up.

577
00:24:57,675 --> 00:24:59,208
别忘了
Neglected to mention

578
00:24:59,210 --> 00:25:02,044
Ramon没被抓到 是因为Percy救了他
that Ramon didn't get busted because she saved him.

579
00:25:02,046 --> 00:25:03,082
你打电话给Pride吗
You calling Pride?

580
00:25:03,106 --> 00:25:05,014
不 打给FBI 我觉得这小子有问题
No, FBI. I got a bad feeling about this guy.

581
00:25:05,015 --> 00:25:06,447
我要明确知道我们面对的是什么人
I want to know exactly who we're dealing with,

582
00:25:06,449 --> 00:25:08,784
这也是为了Percy好 就是说
for Percy's sake. Which means...

583
00:25:08,786 --> 00:25:09,851
如果你还没觉得有必要
if you haven't felt the urge

584
00:25:09,853 --> 00:25:11,452
黑进ATF的数据库
to hack into the ATF database,

585
00:25:11,454 --> 00:25:13,155
拿到卧底行动资料的话
get access to our undercover ops,

586
00:25:13,157 --> 00:25:15,257
现在正是好时机 我就随口一说
now would be the time-- just sayin'.

587
00:25:15,259 --> 00:25:18,559
但那么做不是非法的吗 Gregorio探员
But isn't that illegal, Agent Gregorio?

588
00:25:19,729 --> 00:25:21,628
不问也不说 对么
Don't ask, don't tell, right?

589
00:25:21,630 --> 00:25:22,963
那真的是伤了我的心
That really did a number on me.

590
00:25:22,965 --> 00:25:25,499
我吃不下 睡不着
I didn't eat, couldn't sleep.

591
00:25:25,501 --> 00:25:27,268
我骑车走遍了德州 内华达州
You know I was riding around Texas, Nevada,

592
00:25:27,270 --> 00:25:29,203
一直到加州 就为了找你
all the way out to California trying to find you?

593
00:25:30,673 --> 00:25:34,374
我现在就在这儿啊 不是吗
Well, I'm here now, aren't I?

594
00:25:38,546 --> 00:25:40,180
迟到总比不到好
Well, it's better late than never.

595
00:25:46,855 --> 00:25:48,321
你不能一直躲着她
Can't keep avoiding her, you know.

596
00:25:48,323 --> 00:25:49,488
我知道 但是她也不能
Yeah, I know, but she can't keep

597
00:25:49,490 --> 00:25:50,589
没完没了地打电话
calling all the time, either.

598
00:25:50,591 --> 00:25:51,891
我得工作啊
I gotta focus on work.

599
00:25:51,893 --> 00:25:54,759
工作不是借口 Chris
Work isn't always an excuse, Chris.

600
00:25:54,761 --> 00:25:57,095
你对这个女孩有多了解
How well you know this girl?

601
00:25:57,097 --> 00:26:00,232
一般
Not very.

602
00:26:00,234 --> 00:26:01,800
这就是问题所在
I mean, that's the problem.

603
00:26:01,802 --> 00:26:03,869
你知道Savannah死后
Look, you know how I used to be,

604
00:26:03,871 --> 00:26:05,237
我成了什么样子
after Savannah's death.

605
00:26:05,239 --> 00:26:07,105
那是段黑暗的日子 到处约炮
It was dark times, sleeping around.

606
00:26:07,107 --> 00:26:08,373
这不是什么光彩的事情
It's not something I'm proud of.

607
00:26:08,375 --> 00:26:10,842
我也迷失了自己
And it's not who I am anymore, either.

608
00:26:10,844 --> 00:26:12,476
但是
But...

609
00:26:15,315 --> 00:26:18,382
我真的不知道该怎么办
I honestly don't know what to do.

610
00:26:19,418 --> 00:26:24,088
可我也不能放手不管啊
Still, I can't just... walk away.

611
00:26:24,090 --> 00:26:26,924
但我不知道自己有没有准备好
But I don't know if I'm ready for all this.

612
00:26:26,926 --> 00:26:29,625
我必须得问一句
I gotta ask--

613
00:26:29,627 --> 00:26:30,927
你确定孩子是你的么
you sure the baby's yours?

614
00:26:30,929 --> 00:26:33,230
他长得很像我
Boy, he looks like me.

615
00:26:33,232 --> 00:26:36,532
时间也合得上
And the math definitely works.

616
00:26:36,534 --> 00:26:37,968
这种情况唯一的解决方法就是
Then the only way to deal with something like this

617
00:26:37,970 --> 00:26:39,169
直接面对
is head-on.

618
00:26:39,171 --> 00:26:42,172
这对孩子的母亲来说也不容易
It can't be easy for the mom, either.

619
00:26:42,174 --> 00:26:45,440
但是有一点
But one thing's for sure...

620
00:26:45,442 --> 00:26:47,943
你不能逃避
it's not something you can avoid.

621
00:26:49,080 --> 00:26:50,379
给她打电话吧
Call her back.

622
00:26:50,381 --> 00:26:52,614
我去Sebastian那边看看
I'll see where Sebastian's at.

623
00:26:59,891 --> 00:27:03,958
我不会给你压力的 Sebastian
Hate to pressure you, Sebastian, all right?

624
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,693
你有什么就说什么吧
I'll take anything you got.

625
00:27:05,695 --> 00:27:07,595
我得到的结果 你可能不会喜欢
Well, what I got, I don't think you're gonna like.

626
00:27:07,597 --> 00:27:09,764
我把简易爆炸装置进行了重组
I reassembled most of the IED,

627
00:27:09,766 --> 00:27:12,200
要么嫌疑犯掌握了原始的谷歌技术
and either your bomber's got pristine Googling skills,

628
00:27:12,202 --> 00:27:14,002
要么他有很强的军事背景
or he's got a military background.

629
00:27:14,004 --> 00:27:15,836
好吧 关于爆炸物呢
Okay, well, what about the explosives?

630
00:27:15,838 --> 00:27:17,105
还有更多的坏消息
That's more bad news.

631
00:27:17,107 --> 00:27:18,506
它跟你从建筑工地带回来的
It's a perfect match to the sample

632
00:27:18,508 --> 00:27:19,806
样本完全一致
you brought back from the construction site.

633
00:27:19,808 --> 00:27:21,841
毫无疑问了
I mean, there's no doubt about it.

634
00:27:23,779 --> 00:27:25,845
我不想相信这一切
I don't want to believe that.

635
00:27:25,847 --> 00:27:27,447
为什么这些老兵们
Why would the vets come back here

636
00:27:27,449 --> 00:27:30,951
这么多年后回来 要再卷入
after all these years just to get sucked back into

637
00:27:30,953 --> 00:27:33,353
当初赶走他们的事件 只会更糟
what drove 'em out in the first place, only worse?

638
00:27:33,355 --> 00:27:36,222
过去的恩怨不易了结
Well, old grudges die hard.

639
00:27:37,325 --> 00:27:38,891
没人比你更支持
Nobody's done more to support veterans

640
00:27:38,893 --> 00:27:40,626
退役军人了 Dwayne
than you have, Dwayne.

641
00:27:40,628 --> 00:27:41,961
可你救不了他们全部
You just can't save 'em all.

642
00:27:41,963 --> 00:27:43,762
我知道
I know.

643
00:27:43,764 --> 00:27:47,766
如果是真的 这太令人失望了
Still, it's disappointing, if it's true.

644
00:27:47,768 --> 00:27:51,670
一条臭鱼腥了一锅汤
Something like this stains the whole veteran community.

645
00:27:51,672 --> 00:27:53,471
你打算怎么办
What are you gonna do?

646
00:27:53,473 --> 00:27:57,508
就剩一条路了 逮捕Hogan队长
What I have to do-- arrest Captain Hogan.

647
00:28:11,490 --> 00:28:13,523
ATF的档案显示Percy在两年前的一起枪支运输案件中
ATF says Percy was UC on a gun-running pipeline

648
00:28:13,525 --> 00:28:14,724
当卧底
about two years back.

649
00:28:14,726 --> 00:28:16,493
这位骑手 他只是修摩托车的
Easy Rider, he just fixed bikes.

650
00:28:16,495 --> 00:28:18,996
偶尔也参与运输 但只是个小角色
He did the occasional run, but he was a small fish.

651
00:28:18,998 --> 00:28:21,865
Percy跟他演了场戏 从而打入团伙内部
Percy played the player so she could get in.

652
00:28:21,867 --> 00:28:24,634
就这些么 她的案件陈述里没有其他关于Ramon的内容了
That's it? Nothing else in her case file on Ramon?

653
00:28:24,636 --> 00:28:27,337
没了 事实上 她几乎没怎么提起过他
No. In fact, she barely mentioned him at all.

654
00:28:27,339 --> 00:28:29,405
你们在FBI那边找到他的资料了么
Did you guys find anything on him at the FBI?

655
00:28:29,407 --> 00:28:30,773
只是些零碎的资料
Just some petty stuff.

656
00:28:30,775 --> 00:28:32,075
我的直觉还是不变
Still doesn't change my gut on the guy.

657
00:28:32,077 --> 00:28:33,476
他跟那些坏蛋混在一起
Hangs out with too many bad guys

658
00:28:33,478 --> 00:28:35,311
但Percy却不认为他同流合污
without being dirtier than Percy thinks he is.

659
00:28:35,313 --> 00:28:36,545
爱情真让人盲目
Love is blind.

660
00:28:36,547 --> 00:28:38,481
是啊 又聋又哑
Yeah, deaf and dumb, too.

661
00:28:38,483 --> 00:28:40,816
Pride 我开免提了
Pride, you're on speaker.

662
00:28:40,818 --> 00:28:42,018
Sonja还好吧
Is Sonja okay?

663
00:28:42,020 --> 00:28:43,886
Percy吗 好着呢 怎么了
Percy? Yeah, why? What's wrong?

664
00:28:43,888 --> 00:28:44,853
Hogan失踪了
Hogan's missing.

665
00:28:44,855 --> 00:28:46,554
我们刚刚去抓他
We just went to bring him in,

666
00:28:46,556 --> 00:28:47,589
却在工地后边的沟里
found his bike in a ditch

667
00:28:47,591 --> 00:28:49,024
发现了他的摩托车
behind the construction site,

668
00:28:49,026 --> 00:28:50,425
车上还有新鲜的血迹
fresh blood on the tank,

669
00:28:50,427 --> 00:28:51,659
还有离开的轮胎印
tire tracks leading away.

670
00:28:51,661 --> 00:28:52,861
Sebastian在跟进
Put Sebastian on it.

671
00:28:52,863 --> 00:28:54,296
你认为是骑行帮绑架了他
You think the Niners kidnapped him?

672
00:28:54,298 --> 00:28:55,830
我想不到其它可能了
I don't know what else to think.

673
00:28:55,832 --> 00:28:58,233
我们已经发出了Hogan的协查通报 现在我们正
We got a BOLO out on Hogan now, and we're headed over

674
00:28:58,235 --> 00:28:59,234
开往退役军人俱乐部
to the vets' clubhouse to see

675
00:28:59,236 --> 00:29:00,435
看他们知道或看见些什么
if they know or saw anything.

676
00:29:00,437 --> 00:29:02,703
事态严重了
I don't like where this is heading.

677
00:29:02,705 --> 00:29:03,937
如果骑行帮捉了Hogan
If the Niners took Hogan,

678
00:29:03,939 --> 00:29:05,672
事情很快会恶化
things could get ugly real quick.

679
00:29:05,674 --> 00:29:07,208
我们不能让Sonja被困在其中
We can't let Sonja get caught up in the middle of it.

680
00:29:07,210 --> 00:29:09,877
我来解决 我们得通知Percy
I'm on it. We gotta get word to Percy.

681
00:29:09,879 --> 00:29:12,579
骑行帮刚刚来了
The Niners gang just came up

682
00:29:12,581 --> 00:29:15,016
找Roman问话呢
to Ramon asking for something.

683
00:29:15,018 --> 00:29:16,984
看上去有事要发生 我去弄明白是什么事儿
Looks like something's going down-- I'll find out what.

684
00:29:16,986 --> 00:29:19,219
啊 亲爱的 下一轮我请
Hey, baby, next round's on me.

685
00:29:19,221 --> 00:29:21,554
呃 有点突发状况
Uh, look, something's come up.

686
00:29:21,556 --> 00:29:22,688
我走不开
I gotta jam.

687
00:29:22,690 --> 00:29:24,790
你走不开 什么意思啊
You gotta jam? What do you mean?

688
00:29:24,792 --> 00:29:26,592
那些人究竟是谁啊
Who are those guys, anyway?

689
00:29:27,729 --> 00:29:29,762
你不想招惹的人 相信我
Nobody you want to piss off, trust me.

690
00:29:29,764 --> 00:29:31,398
我们晚点再联系
Look, we'll have to catch up later.

691
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:33,533
你就这么丢下我吗
Are you just gonna ditch me...

692
00:29:33,535 --> 00:29:35,501
过了这么久才遇见啊
after all this time?

693
00:29:35,503 --> 00:29:37,302
我还以为
And here I was thinking

694
00:29:37,304 --> 00:29:40,139
你想知道我离开的原因呢
you wanted to know why I left.

695
00:29:43,810 --> 00:29:46,412
她在干什么
What is she doing?

696
00:29:46,414 --> 00:29:48,780
你要是现在走了 就永远都不会知道了
Walk away now, you'll never know.

697
00:29:52,552 --> 00:29:56,154
好吧 你可以来 但是 你还带着吗
All right, you can come, but, uh, you still carrying?

698
00:29:58,058 --> 00:29:59,768
靴子里的刀 你还带着吗
The knife in the boot, you still got it?

699
00:29:59,769 --> 00:30:00,322
当然了 怎么了
Yeah, why?

700
00:30:00,346 --> 00:30:02,161
千万别把刀扔了 Percy 不要
Don't give up your knife, Percy. Don't do it.

701
00:30:02,162 --> 00:30:03,827
骑行帮要是搜我们的身发现了武器
Niners pat us down and they find something bad,

702
00:30:03,829 --> 00:30:05,596
我们就完蛋了
we ain't going nowhere good.

703
00:30:05,598 --> 00:30:07,532
当然了
Of course.

704
00:30:15,874 --> 00:30:17,740
相信我 我知道自己在做什么
Trust me, I know what I'm doing.

705
00:30:17,742 --> 00:30:19,242
不行 我们得把她弄出来
Forget that, we gotta get her out of there.

706
00:30:20,745 --> 00:30:21,844
没信号了
The wire's dead.

707
00:30:23,348 --> 00:30:24,847
我现在出去
I'm out.

708
00:30:37,628 --> 00:30:40,696
你好
Excuse me.

709
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:01,913
老兵那边有消息吗
Did you get anything from the vets?

710
00:31:01,915 --> 00:31:03,181
除了他们很生气外 没有了
Other than they're pissed off, no.

711
00:31:03,183 --> 00:31:04,397
但你怎么会跟丢Percy
Now, how could you lose Percy?

712
00:31:04,398 --> 00:31:05,457
