You're supposed to be her backup.

713
00:31:05,458 --> 00:31:06,524
你在说什么 我们没想到
What are you talking about? We didn't know

714
00:31:06,526 --> 00:31:08,259
她会丢掉通信设备
she was gonna dump the wire.

715
00:31:08,261 --> 00:31:09,893
如果她要继续跟着Ramon 就必须这么做
She had to if she was gonna stick with Ramon.

716
00:31:09,895 --> 00:31:11,093
她本可以不跟着他 让他走
She could have let him go without her,

717
00:31:11,095 --> 00:31:13,095
但她是老手 她有办法
but she's a pro, she found a way.

718
00:31:13,097 --> 00:31:14,230
是 但她以为你会保护她
Yeah, but she expected you

719
00:31:14,232 --> 00:31:15,565
像你承诺的一样
to have her back, like you promised.

720
00:31:15,567 --> 00:31:16,599
-好了 -够了 听我说
- All right, - that's enough. Listen...

721
00:31:16,601 --> 00:31:18,067
好吗
All right?

722
00:31:18,069 --> 00:31:19,369
这样无济于事
This isn't getting us anywhere.

723
00:31:19,371 --> 00:31:20,903
不管怎样 Percy已处于那种境地
For better or worse, Percy's put herself

724
00:31:20,905 --> 00:31:23,806
她等着我们去找她
in position-- she's counting on us to find her.

725
00:31:23,808 --> 00:31:25,308
定位她的一次性手机了吗
GPS her burner phone?

726
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:26,876
事实上 一次性手机不容易追踪
Burner phones, by nature, don't track easy,

727
00:31:26,878 --> 00:31:28,943
-但我在想办法 -好吧 尽快
- but I'm working on it. - Well, work faster.

728
00:31:28,945 --> 00:31:30,479
如果骑行帮和Hogan一起出现
If the Niners show up with Hogan,

729
00:31:30,481 --> 00:31:31,746
我不想让她一个人
I don't want her ducking bullets

730
00:31:31,748 --> 00:31:33,215
躲避枪林弹雨去救他
trying to save him by herself.

731
00:31:33,217 --> 00:31:35,717
呦 有人在么
Yo, anybody home?

732
00:31:35,719 --> 00:31:38,753
请告诉我你有所发现
